  - front#1533  merged 2026-06-03  # foundation components
  - front#1537  APPROVED           # diagrams page v2 (Denis fixed + approved)
  - front#1543  APPROVED           # brand hub v2 (Denis fixed + approved)
  - search-hono#332  merged 2026-06-03  # MAR registry + multibrand PN (closes A1, C1, C2)
